#!/usr/bin/env npx browserslist
## https://github.com/browserslist/browserslist

## Explicit matching
maintained node versions
Firefox ESR

## Generic matching
cover 95.45%    #NOTE: This is 2σ in normal distribution.
last 0.5 years  #NOTE: Anything released in the past half-year deserves a chance.
last 2 versions #NOTE: This gives people time to update.

## Exclusions
not dead
not < 0.27%      #NOTE: This is -3σ in normal distribution.
not ie >= 0      #NOTE: We explicitly unsupport IE.
not ie_mob >= 0  #NOTE: We explicitly unsupport IE.
not current node #NOTE: LTSs only.
